The '''''Starseeker''''' was a [[Freighter/Legends|freighter]] used by the [[House Pelagia]] agent [[Pellas Agri]] to travel to [[Lamuir IV]] where he was to deliver information to an associate, [[Janna Pallask]]. The ship landed in [[Docking Bay 10]] at a [[Spaceport/Legends|spaceport]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Lamuir IV]].

